blog.description: An Iron Man fan in mourning. Thank you, my darling. We'll all take care of Morgan for you. I love you 3000.

summary: Sadly heavily pixelated, but this is supposed to be Tony’s Avengers 4 armour. It’s called “Mark 85″ The Infinity War suit was...
caption:
Sadly heavily pixelated, but this is supposed to be Tony’s Avengers 4 armour.

It’s called “Mark 85″

The Infinity War suit was Mark 50

HOW FUCKING STRESSED AND DEPRESSED DOES TONY HAVE TO BE TO MAKE 35 SUITS IN ORDER TO GET  READY TO TAKE REVENGE ON THE SPACE PRUNE???

I hereby dub the suit the “Spiderling-Revenger suit” cause let’s face it. Thanos killed Tony’s Spider-Son, therefore Thanos is 125.9999% fucked.
